        "en": "Chapter 1. Demand &amp; Supply<br>Chapter 2. Elasticities of Supply and Demand and Equilibrium<br>Chapter 3. Consumer Behavior<br>Chapter 4. Producer Behavior<br>Chapter 5. National Income<br>Chapter 6. Economic Indicators<br>Chapter 7. Economic Growth"
